collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXpriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=2e5acdc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXpriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=604e1853\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"21ace6b69a180b5305419eca36404ab4c0371c52","tid":1726863,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:29:04.000Z","msg":"我地要做既係美國戰線阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n快上twitter<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本地藍屍撐由佢地，佢係係咪都奶共架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好大件事 唔好玩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國國會美中經濟與安全審議委員會發表年度報告，表示若果中國對香港出動解放軍或武警干預香港局勢，美國國會應該撤銷《美國-香港政策法》給予香港獨立關稅區的特殊地位。"},{"pid":"880c0f4ca8e64698daf7edfc2bd54b9ea5960e6c","tid":1726863,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:29:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d73681568999ef0fbadcec80eacec7b16527591b","tid":1726863,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:29:42.000Z","msg":"唔好因為踩popo就贊老解"},{"pid":"90efbda5bb4db231fb0fac52c49f40db8e80451e","tid":1726863,"uid":262899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:30:23.000Z","msg":"兩者都唔需要"},{"pid":"96af8f5cfc5f265d587b6a4b8482db1673a06e0c","tid":1726863,"uid":271857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:58:38.000Z","msg":"受儒家文化影響，藍絲自小就被洗腦要維護族群最大嗰個。同情做壞事的權貴，某程度是斯德哥爾摩症後群。<br />\n<br />\n儒家文化沒有提及民主自由，而是剛剛相反的輩分尊卑(尊權和卑賤)之分。<br />\n卑賤的人無地方表達和伸張，就會以尊權去發洩在後生一代，然後一代又一代的斯症後群。<br />\n<br />\n中國獨尊儒術，不會容納其他哲學思想，相反西方人會接納不同哲學，百家齊放。儒家文化再加上共產黨，就變得尊上加尊，互補不足，極度尊橫封閉的社會。"}]}